ve…"}, {"id": 164, "slug": "i-am-sorry", "title": "I AM SORRY", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "I AM SORRY"}, {"id": 167, "slug": "i-refuse", "title": "I REFUSE", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "I REFUSE"}, {"id": 169, "slug": "ill-stand-by-you", "title": "I'LL STAND BY YOU", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "I'LL STAND BY YOU"}, {"id": 171, "slug": "if-given-a-chance", "title": "IF GIVEN A CHANCE", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "IF GIVEN A CHANCE"}, {"id": 205, "slug": "is-there-a-time", "title": "IS THERE A TIME", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "IS THERE A TIME"}, {"id": 206, "slug": "it-hurts-like-hell", "title": "IT HURTS LIKE HELL", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "IT HURTS LIKE HELL To pretend that the breakup of a significant relationship Doesn't hurt, is nothing short of self-deception It is lying to one's…"}, {"id": 220, "slug": "kindness-or-judgment", "title": "KINDNESS OR JUDGMENT", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "KINDNESS OR JUDGMENT Sadly, our go-to posture when encountering the unfamiliar Whether that’s a person or a situation Is to evaluate or judge before being…"}, {"id": 248, "slug": "love-alone", "title": "LOVE ALONE", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "LOVE ALONE LOVE HEALS ALL THINGS LOVE NEVER LEAVES LOVE UNDERSTANDS ALL PAIN LOVE WILL ALWAYS BE, NEVER BEGINNING, NEVER ENDING LOVE ALWAYS INCLUDES AND…"}, {"id": 254, "slug": "love-without-pain-des-not-exist", "title": "LOVE WITHOUT PAIN DES NOT EXIST", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "LOVE WITHOUT PAIN DOES NOT EXIST Genuine love, unconditional love, will experience pain If for no other reason than the pain of witnessing Those we…"}, {"id": 266, "slug": "meaningful-encounters", "title": "MEANINGFUL ENCOUNTERS", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "MEANINGFUL ENCOUNTERS It begins with self-understanding A process that's never ending Understanding that we are more alike than unalike Then with more clarity, deeper perception…"}, {"id": 267, "slug": "meaningless-words", "title": "MEANINGLESS WORDS", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "MEANINGLESS WORDS Words