", "excerpt": "THE CONSCIOUSNESS TRIAD Within the realm of consciousness there are three subsets Cognitive consciousness, how we think Affective consciousness, how we feel Spiritual consciousness, how…"}, {"id": 523, "slug": "the-presence-of-one", "title": "THE PRESENCE OF ONE", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "THE PRESENCE OF THE ONE IN THE IN FANTS COOING – THERE IS THE ONE IN THE CHILDS LAUGHTER – THERE IS THE ONE IN…"}, {"id": 538, "slug": "the-shadow-of-america", "title": "THE SHADOW OF AMERICA", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "THE SHADOW OF AMERICA"}, {"id": 542, "slug": "the-tears-of-my-soul", "title": "THE TEARS OF MY SOUL", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "THE TEARS OF MY SOUL The pain I can't acknowledge The tears I can't shed They are held in my soul, with tenderness, in silence…"}, {"id": 590, "slug": "the-five-freedoms", "title": "The Five Freedoms", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "The Five Freedoms - Virginia Satir 1. TO SEE AND HEAR What is here, Instead of what should be, Was, or will be 2. TO…"}, {"id": 615, "slug": "voiceless", "title": "VOICELESS", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "VOICELESS"}, {"id": 621, "slug": "we-dont-know", "title": "WE DON'T KNOW", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "WE DON'T KNOW"}, {"id": 626, "slug": "we", "title": "WE", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "WE We laugh We cry We hurt We have pain and disappointments We all do, regardless of ethnicity, of gender, of color…"}, {"id": 635, "slug": "what-happened-to-humility", "title": "WHAT HAPPENED TO HUMILITY", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "ARE THERE ANY HUMBLE PEOPLE?"}, {"id": 657, "slug": "when-you-think-theres-nothing-left", "title": "WHEN YOU THINK THERE'S NOTHING LEFT", "type": "poem", "excerpt": "WHEN YOU THINK THERE’S NOTHING LEFT There is, and here’s the secret You won’t find it outside of yourself, it’s onside of you, waiting We…"}]